members.name: key
members.description: Specify what key to use in session storage

members.name: setItem
members.description: set the value of session storage for the given or inferred key.

members.name: keyFormat
members.description:
If no key is set, will take the key from the localName of the custom element.
This parameter specifies if that localName should be formatted according to some common rules.
            Possible values:

            
            CamelCase
            
            as-is
            
            camelCase
